<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<body>
    <div class="header-banner">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="banner">
                <div class="indent">
                    <h2 class="indent-left margin-bot" style="margin-left:80px">Tatil & Seyahat Bloğum</h2>
                    <div class="banner-left">
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/glass.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Restaurantlar</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/flight.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Uçuşlar</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/group.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Yapılacaklar</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="con-text">
                            <div class="grid1-img">
                                <img src="~/web/images/key.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid1-desc">
                                <p>Araba Kiralama</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="clear"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="header_bottom_right_images">

                        <div class="slider" style="width:650px; height:400px">
                            <ul class="rslides" id="slider1">
                                @foreach (var x in Model)
                                {
                                    <li><img src="@x.BlogImage" alt="" style="width:650px; height:400px"></li>
                                }
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="clear"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class"content">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="wrapper">
                <div class="con-top">
                    <h3>Tatil Seyahat Bloğuma Hoşgeldiniz!</h3>
                    <p>It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using 'Content here, content here', making it look like readable English.</p>
                </div>
                @Html.Action("Partial1", "Default")
                <div class="grids">
                    <div class="box1">
                        @Html.Action("Partial3", "Default")
                        
                        <div class="clear"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


